{"title":"Python 学习笔记_2：判断 str 类型的函数","slug":"Python学习笔记_2：判断str类型的函数","date":"2020-06-17","updated":"2020-06-17","comments":true,"path":"api/posts/57588.json","excerpt":"<p> 相信大家都喜欢表情包吧 </p><p> 话说学习 Python 一定要坚持，持之以恒，万事开头难嘛 </p><p></p><p> 哈哈，稍微皮一下 </p>","cover":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2020030218253379.png","covers":["https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2020030218253379.png","https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200302221055518.png","https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200302220305485.png"],"content":"<p> 相信大家都喜欢表情包吧 </p>\n<p> 话说学习 Python 一定要坚持，持之以恒，万事开头难嘛 </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2020030218253379.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<p> 哈哈，稍微皮一下 </p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p> 经过整理 </p>\n<p> 今天给大家介绍一下 python 中可以判断 str 类型的函数：</p>\n<p>1、isdigit： 判断 str 是否为数字 </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>I = <span class=\"string\">'123'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>print(I.isdigit())</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> I.isdigit():</span><br><span class=\"line\">&gt;&gt;&gt;\t\tprint(<span class=\"string\">'yes'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">% 输出结果为 </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"literal\">True</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>2、isalpha：判断 str 是否为字母 </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>I = <span class=\"string\">'Abc'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>print(I.isalpha())</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> I.isalpha()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>\tprint(<span class=\"string\">'yes'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">% 输出结果为 </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"literal\">True</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>3、isalnum：判断 str 是否为字母或数字 </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>I = <span class=\"string\">'A2c'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>print(I.isalnum())</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> I.isalnum()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>\tprint(<span class=\"string\">'yes'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">% 输出结果为 </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"literal\">True</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>4、islower：判断 str 是否为小写 </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>I = <span class=\"string\">'abc'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>print(I.islower())</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> I.islower()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>\tprint(<span class=\"string\">'yes'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">% 输出结果为 </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"literal\">True</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>5、isupper：判断 str 是否为大写 </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>I = <span class=\"string\">'ABC'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>print()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> I.isupper()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>\tprint(<span class=\"string\">'yes'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">% 输出结果为 </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"literal\">True</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>6、istitle：判断 str 是否仅有首字母大写 </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>I = <span class=\"string\">'Abc Def'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>print()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> I.istitle()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>\tprint(<span class=\"string\">'yes'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">% 输出结果为 </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"literal\">True</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>7、isspace：判断 str 是否为空格符 </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>I = <span class=\"string\">''</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>print()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"keyword\">if</span> I.isspace()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>\tprint(<span class=\"string\">'yes'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">% 输出结果为 </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"literal\">True</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<hr>\n<hr>\n<hr>\n<p> 看完梨泰院的第 10 集，心情复杂…唉 <br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200302221055518.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<p> 喝杯咖啡再回来继续更博文 <br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200302220305485.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n","url":"/posts/57588/","min2read":1,"word4post":364,"prev_post":{"title":"Python 学习笔记_3：python 列表的使用方法—详细","url":"/posts/36135/"},"next_post":{"title":"Python 学习笔记_1：print 中 end 的用法 print（‘’，end=''）","url":"/posts/54779/"},"toc":"","categories":[{"name":"python","path":"api/categories/python.json","url":"/categories/python/"},{"name":"语法笔记","path":"api/categories/语法笔记.json","url":"/categories/python/语法笔记/"}],"tags":[{"name":"python","path":"api/tags/python.json","url":"/tags/python/"},{"name":"语法笔记","path":"api/tags/语法笔记.json","url":"/tags/语法笔记/"}]}